terraform allows saving a plan to a file

terraform plan -out  infra.plan

after change something in resoure.tf if you run
terraform apply infra.plan

you will be see that was before modification resource.tf

infra.plan is a binary file

run terraform show to read the contents in detail

terraform show infra.plan
or
terraform show -json infra.plan
or for pretty view
terraform show -json infra.plan | jq